        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You take on the power of the mountains, becoming more like the natural and magical creatures who inhabit the land you protect.</em></p><p>You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>You gain a &amp;reference[tremorsense] of 60 ft., allowing you to detect creatures by the vibrations they make in the earth.</p></li><li><p>You are immune to the &amp;reference[petrified] condition.</p></li><li><p>You can cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.l3PBmfstaAN5ybn3]{Meld Into Stone}</em>\u00a0as a 3rd level spell without expending a spell slot.</p></li><li><p>You gain a burrowing speed of 5 ft. If you already have one, your burrowing speed increases by 5 ft.</p></li></ul>",
